OL,3,C'Shocking': Starmer responds to racist
OL,4,Cand sexist comments from Met officers
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer has described the
OL,7,Fbehaviour of of Metropolitan Police
OL,8,Fofficers who were secretly filmed
OL,9,Fmaking racist and sexist comments as
OL,10,F"shocking".
OL,12,FReacting to the footage which appeared
OL,13,Fin a BBC Panorama documentary which
OL,14,Faired on Wednesday evening, the prime
OL,15,Fminister said: "I've not yet seen the
OL,16,Ffootage, but I've had it described to
OL,17,Fme, and it's shocking.
OL,19,F"I'm glad the commissioner is
OL,20,Fresponding. He needs to be very robust
OL,21,Fin his response."
