OL,3,C'Shocking': Starmer responds to racist
OL,4,Cand sexist comments from Met officers
OL,6,FNine serving officers, one ex-officer
OL,7,Fand a designated detention officer
OL,8,Ffrom Charing Cross police station are
OL,9,Fall under investigation for gross
OL,10,Fmisconduct over allegations of use of
OL,11,Fexcessive force and making
OL,12,Fdiscriminatory and misogynistic
OL,13,Fcomments, and failing to report or
OL,14,Fchallenge inappropriate behaviour.
OL,16,FMet Commissioner Sir Mark Rowley spoke
OL,17,Fout on Wednesday ahead of the
OL,18,Fdocumentary airing, stating it is
OL,19,Flikely that all the accused serving
OL,20,Fofficers will be sacked within weeks.
