OL,6,FSir Mark said: "Officers behaving in
OL,7,Fsuch appalling, criminal ways, let
OL,8,Fdown our communities and will cause
OL,9,Fsome to question if their sons and
OL,10,Fdaughters are safe in our cells, and
OL,11,Fwhether they would be believed and
OL,12,Frespected as victims of crime.
OL,14,F"For that, I am truly sorry.
