OL,3,C'Shocking': Starmer responds to racist
OL,4,Cand sexist comments from Met officers
OL,6,F"In line with our uncompromising
OL,7,Fapproach, within 48 hours of these
OL,8,Fallegations being received, nine
OL,9,Fofficers and one staff member had been
OL,10,Fsuspended, with two more officers
OL,11,Fremoved from frontline duties.
OL,13,F"It's my expectation that for those
OL,14,Finvolved, where there is
OL,15,Fincontrovertible evidence of racism,
OL,16,Fmisogyny, anti-Muslim sentiment or
OL,17,Fbragging about excessive use of force,
OL,18,Fthey will be put on a fast-track
OL,19,Fhearing within weeks and on a path to
OL,20,Flikely dismissal."
