OL,3,C'Shocking': Starmer responds to racist
OL,4,Cand sexist comments from Met officers
OL,6,FOn Tuesday, watchdog the Independent
OL,7,FOffice for Police Conduct (IOPC),
OL,8,Fwhich has launched its own inquiry
OL,9,Finto the claims, said that 11 current
OL,10,Fand former officers were under
OL,11,Finvestigation for potential gross
OL,12,Fmisconduct.
OL,14,FOne constable was also under criminal
OL,15,Finvestigation, accused of perverting
OL,16,Fthe course of justice.
OL,18,FThe alleged incidents are said to have
OL,19,Foccurred while those said to have been
OL,20,Finvolved were both on and off duty
OL,21,Fbetween August 2024 and January 2025.
