OL,6,FThe entire custody team at Charing
OL,7,FCross has been disbanded and moved
OL,8,Felsewhere in the wake of the
OL,9,Fallegations, which emerged after an
OL,10,Finvestigation by Panorama.
OL,12,FNine officers at the centre of the
OL,13,Fclaims have been suspended while the
OL,14,FIOPC inquiry continues.
